Name: Spidded
About the game: A hungry spider, dodging a fly swatter, tries to confuse flies in a web and devour them, but difficult levels and an unstable web confuse all his plans. Spidded - An arcade platformer in which the player acts as a spider that moves with its web, dodging a fly swatter and balancing on an unstable web. Features of the game: - Agility Training - Beautiful Pixel-Art - Complexity
